SEARCH
Package com.Bean

Class BeanUserDetails

java.lang.Object
com.Bean.BeanUserDetails
public class BeanUserDetails extends Object
Represents user details in the application. This class encapsulates information about a user, including personal details, contact information, and lists of alternative contacts.

This class provides methods to get and set user attributes.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Sahana
